{% doc %}
  @prompt
    What I need is a comparison table. Firstly, there will be a central heading, with a paragraph underneath, and then a 'compare' button under that. 
    
    Under the compare button will be up to 5 products. You can select up to two at a time. When selected, it will be outlined in red. The products will have their image, maybe able to add an app's trust badges, the name of the product, the price, a little description, some stats next to eachother (column-like), and a learn more button. 
    
    When at least one scooter is selected, when you click the compare button, a table will show up underneath.
    
    Maybe to select there is a button in the top left of the product card.
    
    The table will have up to 10 fields and be based on the product. At the bottom of the table, there will be buttons to learn more about the scooter. Just keep the button simple, saying 'Learn more'. 
    
    I don't want to use the full width of the page. Keep some padding
    
    Make it good for mobile viewing of the table
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-comparison-table-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .ai-comparison-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ settings.heading_font.weight }};
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-comparison-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  {% comment %}
    Desktop / tablet: grid layout
  {% endcomment %}
  .ai-comparison-products-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    padding: 0 100px;
    align-items: stretch;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-comparison-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    background: {{ block.settings.card_background_color }};
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    border-radius: {{ settings.block_border_radius }}px;
    padding: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-comparison-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.selected {
    border-color: {{ block.settings.selection_color }};
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .ai-comparison-select-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    left: 12px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.selection_color }};
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-comparison-select-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}.selected {
    background: {{ block.settings.selection_color }};
  }

